1 care review boards; and
2 (5) Evaluate and make annual recommendations to the Supreme Court, the Legislative
3 Research Commission for referral to the Interim Joint Committee on Families
4 and Children, and the Governor regarding:
5 (a) Laws of the Commonwealth;
6 (b) Practices, policies, and procedures within the Commonwealth affecting
7 permanence for children in out-of-home placement and the investigation of
8 allegations of abuse and neglect;
9 (c) The findings of the local citizen foster care review board community forums
10 conducted pursuant to KRS 620.270; and
11 (d) The effectiveness or lack thereof and reasons therefor of local citizen foster
12 care review of children in the custody of the cabinet in bringing about
13 permanence for the Commonwealth's children.
